      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a legacy of meticulous care, offering an ownership experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning driver to acquire a vehicle in an exemplary state of preservation.",
