    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute mint condition and has been pampered since day one. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! Honestly, it's hard to find one kept this clean. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm sure the next owner will fall in love instantly. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
