    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to pass this beauty on to a new home. It\u2019s been kept in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for your next big adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
