      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-tier condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain is perfectly timed with a recently overhauled VANOS system, ensuring optimal cam phasing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is verified with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping and bushing compliance. Finished in flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle displays no oxidation and zero deferred maintenance. A true turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
